error.message: Declaration of Drupal\semantic_connector\ConnectionListBuilder::buildRow(Drupal\semantic_connector\Entity\SemanticConnectorConnectionInterface $entity) should be compatible with Drupal\Core\Entity\EntityListBuilder::buildRow(Drupal\Core\Entity\EntityInterface $entity)
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to semantic_connector.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
